snippet.title: Paladins x RWBY - Official Collaboration Trailer
snippet.description:
Paladins is getting a crossover with the animated series RWBY in June 2022. Six characters from RWBY will join the team-based shooter as Champion skins. Check out the trailer for the reveal.

#IGN #Paladins #RWBY
